    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That \"software update\" excuse is pretty suspicious. I'm looking at the manifest right now and there was a flag for a customs hold on this route earlier today. If this shipment is sitting in a warehouse or stuck at a border, you need to tell me right now. If we find out later that it was a documentation issue and not \"traffic,\" we're going to be filing a massive claim for the missed surgeries. Is there anything else I should know?",
